fil a group of desires) and sees if=\r\n that tempts one and one stops or one can progress further.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;D=\r\nIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;=\r\n&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;So w=\r\nhat siddhis one gets or does not get, is a function of (1) one&#39;s spiritual =\r\nprogress now AND (2) all of one&#39;s desires until now (in this life AND previ=\r\nous lives). At the same level of progress, two people may fare differently =\r\nin terms of what they get, based on what kind of wishes they entertained in=\r\n the past.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 fa=\r\nce=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 si=\r\nze=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;So siddhis cannot be used to measure one&#39;s progress. =\r\nYou cannot use reverse of f(x, y) to gauge x, without knowing y.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DI=\r\nV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/=\r\nFONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana=\r\n&gt;Best regards,&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D=\r\n2 face=3DVerdana&gt;Narasimha&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#00=\r\n0000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;----------------------------------------------=\r\n---------------------&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 =\r\nsize=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp; Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons,=\r\n Jyotish Writings,&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 siz=\r\ne=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pi=\r\ntri Tarpana:&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 